{"tid":2359413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：正研起訴丹麥國會議員助許智峯流亡","createTime":"2021-01-09T01:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T05:36:07.000Z","uid":21470,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"43c2767c2c9944aa83894a9f922f5dfbff838588","tid":2359413,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:40:43.000Z","msg":"港府據報正研究起訴兩名丹麥政客　兩人被指協助許智峯流亡 <br />\n<br />\n香港政府據報正研究起訴2名丹麥國會議員，指2人協助前立法會議員許智峯流亡至歐洲。丹麥傳媒報道，香港當局正研究引渡2名丹麥政客，分別是左翼「獨立綠黨」和「保守黨」的國會議員。2人據報被指提供虛假的環保會議邀請，令許智峯得以掩飾流亡的意圖。 <br />\n<br />\n丹麥傳媒指，香港政府向當地報章確認，正研究有甚麼法律選項，處理協助許智峯流亡的人士。不過，現時香港和丹麥沒有引渡安排的協議。報道指，丹麥外長表示，丹麥政客可以與他們想見的任何人見面，不必擔心遭到報復，政府會完全捍衛這項權利。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2374041&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=4e70a7d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2374041</a>"},{"pid":"35b05d1dbd592f331d80c7e74d16fb88db710994","tid":2359413,"uid":317979,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T01:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7pHeRm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7pHeRm.gif&h=bb52b425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efb0a6a214e7577adef746d9fbfa508513f407b2","tid":2359413,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我<br />\n封澳州之後瀨撚哂野仲唔識死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ab9066fa92a7287b66c18db4fd13ef934f0df0","tid":2359413,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"歐洲、支那單deal要過歐洲議會 www"},{"pid":"335c7f8732a31368ca2a468ec598a5fad3fa33ae","tid":2359413,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T02:08:36.000Z","msg":"派3萬過去囉<br />\n唔係<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span cl